Portugal Plans to Limit Gains in Electricity Prices, Diario Says

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-10-07T06:22:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/portugal-plans-to-limit-rise-in-electricity-prices-diario-says.html
Portuguese Economy Minister Alvaro
Santos Pereira is preparing to put forward a plan that would
limit the increase in electricity prices to about 5 percent,
Diario Economico reported, without saying how it obtained the
information.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
